WEBVTT

00:01:57.480 --> 00:02:00.216
(Robot arm buzzing)

00:02:00.240 --> 00:02:03.456
(Laughter)

00:02:03.480 --> 00:02:06.976
(Applause)

00:02:07.000 --> 00:02:11.536
So my toothbrush helmet is recommended
by zero out of 10 dentists,

00:02:11.560 --> 00:02:15.736
and it definitely did not
revolutionize the world of dentistry,

00:02:15.760 --> 00:02:18.936
but it did completely change my life.

00:02:18.960 --> 00:02:22.416
Because I finished making this toothbrush
helmet three years ago

00:02:22.440 --> 00:02:23.976
and after I finished making it,

00:02:24.000 --> 00:02:26.656
I went into my living room
and I put up a camera,

00:02:26.680 --> 00:02:29.160
and I filmed a seven-second
clip of it working.

00:02:29.760 --> 00:02:30.976
And by now,